fy.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/the-concept-of-learning-english-a-notebook-on-a-b-2024-01-16-16-53-08-utc.jpg?v=1709570090" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/the-concept-of-learning-english-a-notebook-on-a-b-2024-01-16-16-53-08-utc.jpg?v=1709570090 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/the-concept-of-learning-english-a-notebook-on-a-b-2024-01-16-16-53-08-utc_1000x.jpg?v=1709570090 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/the-concept-of-learning-english-a-notebook-on-a-b-2024-01-16-16-53-08-utc_500x.jpg?v=1709570090 320w" width="1000" height="667" alt="English Language Day 2024: A Global Celebration of Linguistic Unity - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="English Language Day 2024: A Global Celebration of Linguistic Unity - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fulBNO bzoLbm pf-121_"/><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-122_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by AtlasComposer via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-124_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">English Language Day serves as a reminder of the importance of linguistic diversity and the role of language in fostering global understanding. It provides an opportunity to celebrate the beauty and versatility of the English language while promoting cultural exchange and mutual respect.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-126_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fsvrPk ezIRGP pf-127_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-128_">Key facts and statistics</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/mohdizzuanbinroslan_9189aef4-9d35-452d-b1c1-4af36fbd37ab.jpg?v=1709570155" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/mohdizzuanbinroslan_9189aef4-9d35-452d-b1c1-4af36fbd37ab.jpg?v=1709570155 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/mohdizzuanbinroslan_9189aef4-9d35-452d-b1c1-4af36fbd37ab_1000x.jpg?v=1709570155 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/mohdizzuanbinroslan_9189aef4-9d35-452d-b1c1-4af36fbd37ab_500x.jpg?v=1709570155 320w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Celebrate English Language Day: Embracing Linguistic Diversity Worldwide - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Celebrate English Language Day: Embracing Linguistic Diversity Worldwide - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fulBNO bzoLbm pf-130_"/><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-131_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by mohdizzuanbinroslan via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-fAGzVM iDZITE pf-133_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bkSTSn iEaWBl pf-134_">English is the third most spoken language globally, with over 1.5 billion speakers worldwide.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bkSTSn iEaWBl pf-136_">It is one of the six official languages of the United Nations, emphasising its importance in international diplomacy and communication.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bkSTSn iEaWBl pf-138_">According to the British Council, English is the primary or secondary language of communication for over two billion people worldwide.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bkSTSn iEaWBl pf-140_">English Language Day coincides with the birthday and date of the death of William Shakespeare, highlighting the language's rich literary tradition and cultural significance.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-142_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fsvrPk ezIRGP pf-143_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-144_">How the English Language Day engages learners</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/online-english-school-at-home-serious-guy-in-glas-2023-11-27-04-56-08-utc.jpg?v=1709570266" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/online-english-school-at-home-serious-guy-in-glas-2023-11-27-04-56-08-utc.jpg?v=1709570266 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/online-english-school-at-home-serious-guy-in-glas-2023-11-27-04-56-08-utc_1000x.jpg?v=1709570266 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/online-english-school-at-home-serious-guy-in-glas-2023-11-27-04-56-08-utc_500x.jpg?v=1709570266 320w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Unlock the World Through Linguistic Diversity: English Language Day Insights - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Unlock the World Through Linguistic Diversity: English Language Day Insights - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fulBNO bzoLbm pf-146_"/><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-147_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Prostock-studio via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-fAGzVM iDZITE pf-149_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bkSTSn iEaWBl pf-150_"><b>Promoting multilingualism</b> - English Language Day encourages learners to appreciate the value of multilingualism and cultural diversity. By celebrating the English language alongside other languages, learners gain a deeper understanding of different cultures and perspectives.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bkSTSn iEaWBl pf-152_"><b>Enhancing language skills</b> - For language learners, English Language Day offers an opportunity to practice and improve their English language skills. Through language-themed events, workshops, and activities, learners can immerse themselves in the English language and culture, enhancing their proficiency and fluency.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bkSTSn iEaWBl pf-154_"><b>Cultural exploration</b> - English Language Day provides a platform for learners to explore English literature, history, and culture. From Shakespearean sonnets to contemporary novels, learners can discover the richness and diversity of the English literary tradition, gaining insights into different periods and genres.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-156_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fsvrPk ezIRGP pf-157_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-158_">Organisations supporting English Language Day</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/multicultural-group-of-young-people-standing-and-s-2023-11-27-05-05-18-utc.jpg?v=1709570536" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/multicultural-group-of-young-people-standing-and-s-2023-11-27-05-05-18-utc.jpg?v=1709570536 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/multicultural-group-of-young-people-standing-and-s-2023-11-27-05-05-18-utc_1000x.jpg?v=1709570536 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/multicultural-group-of-young-people-standing-and-s-2023-11-27-05-05-18-utc_500x.jpg?v=1709570536 320w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Master English from Home: Top Tips for Learning English Online - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Master English from Home: Top Tips for Learning English Online - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fulBNO bzoLbm pf-160_"/><p class="sc-bVVHAX cfQUSW pf-161_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by LightFiel